## üß™ Testing

Run the test suite:

```bash
# Install development dependencies
pip install -r requirements-dev.txt

# Run unit tests
pytest tests/unit/

# Run Robot Framework tests
robot tests/robot/acceptance/

# Run all tests
make test
```
